name: Tentakeln
description: My first photo piece on HEN. The oldest and largest tree for miles around is in our backyard. I spent many years as a boy climbing these strong arms and resting in it’s curves. They say it’s likely over 200 years old. My boy enjoys the same experience, with a lift of course... because those first arms are not quite within reach yet. This is a 1/1 from @TheWaldorfJ on Twitter
